  ('optometrist-moex-00484', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列情形下會優先考慮驗配後散光硬式隱形眼鏡鏡片（toroidalbackopticzone）而不是球面硬式隱形眼鏡 鏡片？', '["角膜逆散光不超過0.50D", "從眼睛摘除硬式球面鏡片時，會出現明顯的角膜變形（cornealdistortion）和眼鏡性視力模糊（spectacleblur）", "水平可見虹膜直徑（Horizontalvisibleirisdiameter,HVID）超過11.5mm", "戴球面硬式隱形眼鏡鏡片時，無殘餘散光（noresidualastigmatism）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b745f9722863", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cd693ea90406", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
